author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Wondering if you might benefit from hearing aids? Take Jabra Enhance's online hearing test to see if you’re a candidate at http://JabraEnhance.com/Tested and get $200 off.

We continue a conversation we’ve been having on the channel about Adam's hearing loss, destigmatizing hearing aids, and advances in virtual hearing care. Jabra Enhance–the sponsor of today’s video and the makers of Adam's hearing aids–has made it possible to get hearing assessments online without needing to visit a clinic. Dr. Katie Keese, Jabra Enhance’s Head of Audiology, visited us in the cave to answer questions about at-home audiology and how remote access to hearing care can be life-changing.
